imdb.plot outline: MTV Russia hosts Rita Danielova and Anita Bhoumik attend the Gala opening of "Extending the Runway: Tatiana Sorokko Style" exhibition at the Russian Fashion Museum in Moscow. A lively discussion and review of the show follows with Russia's first supermodel and couture collector Tatiana Sorokko, l'Officiel editor Evelina Khromchenko and fashion designer Vika Gazinskaya.
imdb.title: Trendy
plot: MTV Russia's popular TV show covering trends in latest fashion, life style and night life. Interviews are done throughout the world - Japan, Berlin, Paris, New York and Moscow::Ivan Vasiliev

MTV Russia hosts Rita Danielova and Anita Bhoumik attend the Gala opening of "Extending the Runway: Tatiana Sorokko Style" exhibition at the Russian Fashion Museum in Moscow. A lively discussion and review of the show follows with Russia's first supermodel and couture collector Tatiana Sorokko, l'Officiel editor Evelina Khromchenko and fashion designer Vika Gazinskaya.::Marina Velikanova
